{"tid":37181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老公參加告別單身趴　女老師摩鐵床戰16歲高二生","createTime":"2016-12-13T08:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T10:09:41.000Z","uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"abaf99f290c68f29958e0db29adde2aaf628181c","tid":37181,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:00:19.000Z","msg":"老公參加告別單身趴　女老師摩鐵床戰16歲高二生<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美國威斯康辛州29歲的前高中女教師多姆瑞斯，被指控與16歲的學生發生性關係，其中有一次還是在老公參加告別單身派對的晚上，之後夫妻倆蜜月旅行時，她還將自拍照傳給學生，並在1100條的簡訊中稱對方為「Baby Boo」，「寶貝我愛你，不論是現在或永遠！」<br />\n根據美國《每日新聞》以及《FOX6 NOW》報導，29歲的多姆瑞斯（Sara Domres）原本是威斯康辛州一所高中的老師，她在2014至2015學年間與一名16歲的高二生談戀愛並發生性關係，但她只承認做過2次。<br />\n<br />\n▲多姆瑞斯僅承認與學生做愛2次，對方卻向警方供稱，2人發生10到15次性關係。（圖／翻攝自FOX6 NOW）<br />\n<br />\n該名男學生卻供稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">2人發生大約10到15次的性行為</span>，第一次是2015年7月在當地一處停車場，同年10月又在老師的丈夫參加告別單身派對時到汽車旅館做愛，<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至還在老師蜜月旅行時收到自拍照。</span><br />\n<br />\n檢警發現，多姆瑞斯與男學生互傳的1100條簡訊中，經常以「Baby Boo」稱呼對方，其中一條簡訊還寫著，「寶貝，我愛你不論現在或永遠！也請你成為我的永遠，我是你永遠的寶貝女孩。另外，祝你順利通過測驗。」<br />\n<br />\n消息傳開後多姆瑞斯遭校方開除，她在法庭上崩潰表示，自己對教職很有熱情，失去這份工作讓她感到很後悔。檢方則強調，如果多姆瑞斯的身分不是老師，這件事只會是輕罪，「考慮到老師對學生的權力及影響力，她只能被判定為重罪。」<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20161213/828505.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20161213%2F828505.htm&d=tS4NxEAAFVHhcAG2JL79aZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=82d57d4d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20161213/828505.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8aaf0b1ad8a4822bd555a0af65c1eba10a82cbdf","tid":37181,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322f6531c9bf35bceb469fbc230f99613af05cb8","tid":37181,"uid":61864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"外國真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b779905eec9ddb49f47f74634705342749ba3d","tid":37181,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:09:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">快</span></span>"},{"pid":"65e98878c75eaae1c78cd759bb3ebaba1f37e2c8","tid":37181,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:10:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">快</span>"},{"pid":"66b41ae1218e4b3a3fb3548abb671fd24d00efe0","tid":37181,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">快</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點</span></span>"},{"pid":"579880ff0f5b6b7124acfb73696eb5ca920da80b","tid":37181,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://localtvwiti.files.wordpress.com/2016/04/domres-300.jpg?quality=85&amp;strip=all&amp;w=266\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flocaltvwiti.files.wordpress.com%2F2016%2F04%2Fdomres-300.jpg%3Fquality%3D85%26strip%3Dall%26w%3D266&h=b7b9d9ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a69de59d3b9128e1c76841e5f00baedde8aa3073","tid":37181,"uid":64701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">快</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點</span></span>"},{"pid":"76d5024defc77c178ba106ab61a8e8049321707f","tid":37181,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:15:39.000Z","msg":"停左啦???"},{"pid":"299e56a597b801bd15e392c49b52545ae107247c","tid":37181,"uid":24366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2